      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2000,
          "startTime": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（東京でとある用事を済ませた俺は）\n（見慣れた人物を見つけた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(After I’d taken care of some business in Tokyo‚)\n(I saw a familiar figure.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.366666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 7.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 9.993650786081949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ……\n星見プロの{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…\n{user}-san from Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.993650786081949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さん、こんばんは\n……大丈夫ですか？　元気がないように見えますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good evening‚ Okuyama-san.\n…Are you alright? You look a bit down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.993650786081949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 20.460317452748615
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "……今日はTRINITYAiLEの\nライブだったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There was a TRINITYAiLE\nlive today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.56031745274861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、知ってます。アンコールで歌った新曲\nトリエルらしくてとても良かったですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I know. The new song you sang for the encore\nwas really good‚ and just TRINITYAiLE’s style.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.109883098724566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 30.976549765391233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……\nって、えええええ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so…\nI mean‚ eeeeeh?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8432164320579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 35.109883098724566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nも、もしかして見に来てたっちゃ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nYou mean‚ you came to see us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.109883098724566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEです！\nみなさん、今日は本当にありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We are TRINITYAiLE!\nThank you all so much for coming today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.17654976539124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "こんなにも沢山の方々が集まってくれて\n素敵な時間を共有出来て……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having so many of you gathered together\nto share a great time together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.809883098724576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "私達は世界で一番の幸せ者です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "makes us the happiest people in the world!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.464235317598614,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2799.9999999999973,
          "startTime": 55.26423531759861
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "今日みたいなステージがあるから\nアイドルって楽しいんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being an idol is fun because of\nshows like today’s!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.69756865093194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、準備はいいですか？\n次の曲いきますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ are you ready?\nNext song‚ here we go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.99756865093192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 68.36423531759858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今日のステージでのパフォーマンス\n堂々としていて、凄くかっこ良かったですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your performance at today’s live was\nimpressive‚ and totally cool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.86423531759858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "うわーん！　面と向かって言われると\nなんだか恥ずかしいっちゃ～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa! To be told that to my face\nmakes me feel kind of shy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.85134805165146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 81.61801471831812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ落ち着いて……ところで\n天動さんと鈴村さんは一緒じゃないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Relax… By the way‚\naren’t Tendo-san and Suzumura-san with you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5180147183181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "あ……えっと、マネージャーさんやスタッフさんと\nライブの打ち上げがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ err… there’s an after-show party\nwith the manager and staffs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.45134805165142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 96.08468138498476
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "私も出たかったんですけどね～\n帰りの新幹線の時間がありますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to go too‚ but…\nthen I’d miss the Shinkansen home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.95134805165142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんのマンションに\nお泊まりも出来るんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I could sleep over with\nRui-chan and Yu-chan‚ but …",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.8846813849848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "あまり頻繁だと家族が心配しますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "if I do that too often‚ my family starts to worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.11801471831814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 109.65690364959255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "打ち上げに出られないなんて、寂しいですね\nそれに、せめて誰か途中まで見送ってくれても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you couldn’t go to the party and are feeling lonely.\nI’d have expected someone to at least walk you part of the way back…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.65690364959256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 118.12357031625923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "違うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.12357031625923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんが駅まで送るって\n言ってくれたんですけど、ダメだよって断りました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan and Yu-chan said they want to accompany me to the station‚\nbut I refused.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.19502157094492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 126.99502157094497
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "打ち上げって、私達のために頑張って下さった\n人たちに感謝を伝える場だと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think the after-party is a place for showing our gratitude\nto all the people who worked so hard for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.09502157094497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "だから、瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんまでいなかったら\nみなさんに申し訳ないじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So if even Rui-chan and Yu-chan weren’t there‚\nit would be rude to everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.79502157094507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 139.59502157094505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_03-koh008.m4a",
